OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry, warm
OL,6,Fand bright evening with some hazy
OL,7,Fsunny periods. It will then remain dry
OL,8,Ffor the rest of the night with clear
OL,9,Fspells and light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FEarly morning cloud soon
OL,12,Fburning off to leave another very warm
OL,13,Fand largely sunny day.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FHot
OL,16,Fon Thursday but with the risk of heavy
OL,17,Fand thundery outbreaks of rain later
OL,18,Fin the day and into Friday. Fresher by
OL,19,FSaturday but risk of showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
